hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I hate shopping vitex 500 mg "I just think an uplighter would make a world of difference." "The utility room is a hell hole, it fills me with dread. We need some small storage-baskety type things." "I spent £400 on bedding so I'm more than happy to spend £400 on candles." "I'd like 24 matching white wine glasses and 24 matching red wine glasses." "I think it would be nice to have a really large wooden cutting board, so when we have a roast the juices will flow into the grooves." "We need tea lights, and we need jars to put them in." "Don't laugh at me, you're the one with the strawberry huller." "We need stainless steel pots for herbs, so that it's all matchy-matchy by the sink." "You're right, we do need at least six lampshades."
